'''4-氟丁醇'''是一种有机化合物，为无色的可燃性液体，化学式为C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>9</sub>FO。它可由乙酸-4-羟基丁酯<!-- CAS 35435-68-8 -->经二乙氨基三氟化硫氟化后，用[[氢化铝锂|氢化铝锂]]还原制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemical Communications|issue=31|language=en|issn=1359-7345|date=2005|pages=3983|doi=10.1039/b506635b|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=b506635b|title=A novel fluorinated erythromycin antibiotic|accessdate=2020-11-30|author=Rebecca J. M. Goss, Hui Hong}}</ref>[[1,4-丁二醇|1,4-丁二醇]]和[[四氟化硫|四氟化硫]]的反应虽然也会生成4-氟丁醇，但是也会同时产生[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]]和少量的亚硫酸丁二酯<!-- 环状结构，丁烷的两头连接SO3的两个氧 -->。<ref>Wang, Chia-Lin J. Sulfur tetrafluoride. ''e-EROS Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis'', 2001. 1-2.</ref>它可以被[[戴斯－马丁氧化剂|马丁试剂]]氧化为4-氟丁醛。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Medicinal Chemistry|volume=62|issue=2|language=en|issn=0022-2623|date=2019-01-24|pages=893–907|doi=10.1021/acs.jmedchem.8b01609|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.jmedchem.8b01609|title=Development of Novel Quinoxaline-Based κ-Opioid Receptor Agonists for the Treatment of Neuroinflammation|accessdate=2020-11-30|author=Giovanni Tangherlini, Dmitrii V. Kalinin, Dirk Schepmann, Tao Che, Nadine Mykicki, Sonja Ständer, Karin Loser, Bernhard Wünsch}}</ref>

它和[[2-氟乙醇|2-氟乙醇]]一样，会因其代谢为氟乙酸盐而具有高毒性。<ref>Pattison F. Toxic Fluorine Compounds. ''Nature'' 1953; 172: 1139–1141.{{doi|10.1038/1721139a0}}</ref><ref>Pattison FML, Howell WC, McNamara AJ, Schneider JC, Walker JF. Toxic Fluorine Compounds. III.<sup>1</sup> ω-Fluoroalcohols. ''The Journal of Organic Chemistry'' 1956; 21(7): 739-747. {{doi|10.1021/jo01113a006}}</ref>

